    <body.head>
      <hedline>
        <hl1>The Inclining Laptop</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Letter by Erik Engquist responds to Frederick Willman letter on lack of laptop with an inclining keyboard (June 1 article); says IBM does offer model with such feature</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>To the Editor:</p>
        <p>In a letter on June 1 (Incoming, ''Laptop Innovations''), Frederick Willman said that he would buy a laptop when I.B.M. made one with an inclining keyboard. Time to head to the store: my 4-year-old Thinkpad 760EL's keyboard inclines automatically when the computer is opened.</p>
        <p>ERIK ENGQUIST  Brooklyn</p>
      </block>
      <block class="full_text">
